 *Title*: User can't see an image preview on the "Create Issue" pop-up.
 *Version*: JIRA v7.6.1
 *Browsers*: Chrome 64
 *Preconditions*: Existing user account;

*Steps to Reproduce*:
1. Log in to JIRA;
2. Click on create button; 
3. Drag and drop an image to the "Create Issue" pop-up;
4. Switch to "Text" mode;
5. On the "Description" filed write down {code} "!IMAGE_NAME.png|thumbnail!" {code}

6. Switch to "Visual" mode.

*Actual Results*: 
On the "Visual" mode there is following text: 
{code}No usable issue astores in the context, unable to resolve filename 'IMAGE_NAME.png'{code}
 !image issue.png|thumbnail! 

*Expected Results*: 
There should be uploaded image preview.
